			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">A Damage Bonus (DB) applies to 1H weapons equipped in primary hand and 2H weapons. It does not apply to 1H weapons equipped in secondary hand. It does not increase the effective damage number of your weapon by the amount of the DB; it is a fixed amount of damage added to every successful swing.
<br />

<br />
Melee characters first receive a DB at level 28. The DB for 1H weapons is based on level only, and is approximately equal to (level-25) / 3. The DB for 2H weapons is based on both level and weapon delay. Currently, the DB "sweet spot" for 2H weapons is a delay of 28 (i.e., the DB increases dramatically for 2H weapons with a delay of 28+).
<br />

<br />
Lucy has a chart showing DBs for 1H and 2H weapons at the following URL:
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/dmgbonus.html" target="_blank" class="postlink">Lucy DB Table</a><br />_________________<br /><img src="http://home.comcast.net/~ytrill/ytrill8.jpg" border="0" />
<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27521" target="_blank" class="postlink">Hunter Ytrill Stonebow</a>
<br />
Forest Stalker of Tunare, Grand Master Fletcher
<br />
E'ci
<br />
<img src="http://webpages.charter.net/ytrill/2238crit.gif" border="0" /></span><span class="gentblsmall"></span></td>
